  "title": "Relaxed Shoulders",
  "description": "Subtly animates player arms to look more natural.",
  "body": "<font size=\"32\"> Relaxed Shoulders </font>\n---\n\n\n\nUses EMF to make player's arms more dynamic with physics -> https://www.youtube.com/shorts/2jwR29q3Kfg (video showing jump physics and idle position)\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/9d4f6b90e89d4dd1477f46012f38f53caab39bef_0.webp\" width=\"200\"/>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/eeac1cb3e405dcb42f7c33a7773d195c403914d6_0.webp\" width=\"200\"/>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/bb57a24e6863b2d72d78d9eb6613b63373102f34_0.webp\" width=\"200\"/>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/97f389fdae4716a769c350e48298e4eb59f9c81c_0.webp\" width=\"200\"/>\n</details>\n\n---\nYou'll need optifine or EMF for this pack to work. Make sure to turn this setting ON in EMF settings: models > player settings > prevent first person hand animations\n\n![Replace this with a description](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/2981e153f02f5c13b45881c650683a3244bc1c07.png)\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/entity-model-features\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/328492a8b975e65303039d04d34a3353b3fd45fe.png\" width=\"150\"/>\n</a>\n\n</center>\n",
